{"id":100197,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/【原创】谷歌往事三则/","date":"2010-08-23T15:54:24Z","modified":"2010-08-23T15:54:24Z","title":"【原创】谷歌往事三则","content":"<p><p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/3806538/2\">郭去疾的博客 &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <br />\n<br />发布时间:2010年08月22日,  已有 8 人推荐 </p>\n<hr>\n<div>\n<p><span><span><br />\n谷歌往事三则</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><br />\n（</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></span><span><span>）</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discuz</span></span><span><span>是我当年在谷歌主导的第一个投资，美国总部看不懂，开复和宓群做了不少推动。那时有三家</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">BBS</span></span><span><span>软件公司：</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discuz</span></span><span><span>，动网，</span></span><br />\n<span><span lang=\"EN-US\">PHPWind</span></span><span><span>，分别被周鸿祎、蔡文胜、王定标投资，颇有点“得</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">BBS</span></span><span><span>得天下”的意思。投资过程中与戴志康、鸿祎、红杉张帆有不少沟通，学了不少东西。我一直相信，</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discuz</span></span><span><span>的辉煌将是</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SAAS</span></span><span><span>。据说最近</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discuz</span></span><span><span>被腾讯收购。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><br />\n（</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></span><span><span>）我在谷歌影响的第一个投资是</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">265</span></span><span><span>。当时百度投了好</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">123</span></span><span><span>，谷歌在中国没人，我也还在美国，拜托在卓越亚马逊的刘俊造访蔡文胜，主要是想知道</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IDG</span></span><span><span>哪个合伙人投资的。了解到是过玉红之后，秘群迅速联系了</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">IDG</span></span><span><span>。文胜非常聪明，立刻知道刘俊是牵线人（我们没有讲），投资完成后专门打电话去道谢。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><br />\n（</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></span><span><span>）谷歌音乐签了几百家唱片公司，与</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMI</span></span><span><span>的谈判我和巨鲸网陈戈飞到</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMI Digital</span></span><span><span>伦敦总部。有预言意味的是：作为传统唱片业的掘墓者，我们被邀请造访流行音乐史的丰碑</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Abbey Road</span></span><span><span>录音棚</span></span><span><span>，</span></span><span><span>并在那完成了最后的谈判。</span></span><span>The<br />\nBeatles曾在那里录制了著名的唱片Abbey Road</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://sinaurl.cn/GhRUT\">http://sinaurl.cn/GhRUT</a></span></span><span>。</span><span><span>带我们参观的是一位在那工作了</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span></span><span><span>多年的老太太。当时</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMI</span></span><span><span>刚从</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Google</span></span><span><span>雇了</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Douglas Merrill</span></span><span><span>做</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMI Digital</span></span><span><span>全球总裁，</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Douglas</span></span><span><span>准备把</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">EMI Digital</span></span><span><span>总部从伦敦搬到加州，所以伦敦办公室正风雨飘摇，和我们谈判的两位高层都面临着两个月后被遣散的命运，但他们还是以极大的职业精神与热忱完成了我们的合作。</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.photo.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#url=http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/orignal/62d14892t8e6e8a3c3146\"><img src=\"http://static7.photo.sina.com.cn/bmiddle/62d14892t8e6e8a3c3146&#038;690\" name=\"image_operate_55841282505347596\" /></a></p>\n<p></span></span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/1017243/tongji.gif\" /><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/997968/tongji.gif\" /></p>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://idajiangyou.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8615,8800]}